:::Herald Held up his creation. it was a perfectly round orb of metal. Herald 
Spoke to himself:::

Herald: "This is the Enticron Orb! it will affect the Universe forever. The 
Enticron Orb is a Bomb that has enough power to destroy a Galaxy! Who ever 
holds this will be the dominant Faction in the Neo Beast wars!"

:::A look of worry then crossed his face, What had he done he had just sealed 
the fate of every spark on the planet. He teleported himself to the next 
galaxy. There he found The Matrix, it spoke to him:::

'Give me the orb' herald did, 'Now come into your glory as a god!'

Herald replied: "Not yet Matrix, no but later when the wars are over i will 
become a god, yes, for now I am needed. But Matrix could you give me one 
gift? Could you give me a TM4 Driver?:::Flash::: He was back in his Lab, in 
his hands... the TM4 driver!:::
